These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
House: colonial, palace
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, raspberry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, electronic
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, skateboard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, iris
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, dannemann
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of folk##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
5. the dannemann-smoker is the fan of electronic##1
6. the social-worker is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| House      | palace        | colonial |
| Food          | raspberry  | pineapple     |
| Music-Genre         | electronic    | folk         |
| Job           | analyst    | social-worker |
| Transport   | car  | skateboard     |
| Flower           | iris      | aconite    |
| Cigar         | dannemann | chaman          |

