There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, russian
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bongani
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony
1. the russian is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| House         | art-deco      | townhouse       |
| Game           | go | scrabble |
| Flower   | dahlia      | balloon-flower        |
| Music-Genre   | folk         | trance        |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | russian       |
| Cigar           | bongani        | cain          |
| Color     | ebony          | mauve    |

