.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, november
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, montecristo
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, chestnut
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, scientific
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey
2 different pets are kept: bird, goat
1. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Birthday      | august | november  |
| Cigar          | montecristo   | dunhill   |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | puzzles   |
| Color           | emerald        | chestnut   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific      | horror |
| Sport         | ice-hockey    | climbing  |
| Pet     | bird       | goat      |

